
                             Interview to NexusC
                                by VirusBuster
                            ---------------------


- How old are you? Where do you come from?

20, Sweden

- Why did you start collecting viruses?

I got fascinated after i found various pages regarding viruses/malware and
other undergrouns stuff.

- For how long have you been collecting viruses?

Don't really remember.. Might have been somewhere around 1997-98 i started
but then i didn't have an organized collection or traded, it was mostly
leeching all pages i found and put it all in a folder ;)

I remember i had the whole collection saved on floppies. I had to split the
zip to ~15 floppies.

- Did you ever stop trading viruses and continued after a time? If yes,
  for how long were you inactive?, why did you stop?, why did you decide
  to continue?

I stopped trading compleatly once after i had been on the top (or near it)
since it sucked to only get ~5 files in every trade and maby 15 as most in a
week so i got bored.

The break might have been somewhere near 2 months or so but i got back when
new traders came along and made it possible to make bigger trades once again.

- What are your virus statistics actually? (AVP/F-Prot/... unique/total)

42345 virii for AVP/KAV
41321 unique virii for AVP/KAV

