- Do you make backups of your collection? If yes, How often and what is the
  media you use to make backups?

I back up the folder wich contains all the latest files i've gotten. But i
don't make a backup of it before it fills a whole 700mb cd packed with the
best RAR-compression ;)

After the backup is done i move all files in the folder to the regular bulk
dirs. (I burn with Nero)

