I used vs2k before it became viriiware and since u now have to contribute for
it i think everyone who has contributed should be able to get a free update
if any bugs are found in that version.

I still use vs2k, but i think it's getting more and more stuff that really
don't belong in the tool.

- What is your opinion about the viriiware?

Both good and bad ;)

